image_analysis.description: A high-angle photograph of a desk setup featuring an Apple iMac computer on a bright red glossy desk. The computer screen shows the macOS desktop with the 'System Preferences' window open. On the desk, there is a white keyboard, a white Magic Mouse, a landline telephone, a bottle of hand sanitizer, a wooden tissue box, a cup of pens/pencils, a tape dispenser, and a blue United States passport. In the background, the legs of two individuals are partially visible.
image_analysis.layout: The image is a wide-angle photograph with the computer centered. Objects are scattered across the red desk surface.
